    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors are appropriately not assessed per MRL 2 scope. GCI < 5%, output comparison within 15%, and correct worst-case identification collectively support the claim that the CFD model is credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for this Class II CPB device. Package conforms to ProfileMinimal; digital signature is pending completion of the institutional signature workflow and will be appended prior to regulatory submission.",
